{"tid":1753634,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世] 致各位今次當選區議員","createTime":"2019-11-25T03:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T05:55:11.000Z","uid":122059,"like":106,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"7512d012037a25f77edcb335bb8c07a5f4e5c259","tid":1753634,"uid":122059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"相信有好多當選既區議員都係首次當選 而且又係空降某某區<br />\n今次非建制派大勝 中共係唔會想見到<br />\n我地要逆向思維 佢地手握種票 染紅既選舉主任<br />\n個感覺就好似特登輸咁<br />\n可能有好多人覺得係民意覺醒 共產黨都無計 但希望大家要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">居安思危</span></span><br />\n我地贏左區選 佢就肯定會用之後唔同既手段搞9我地 大家要穩住陣腳 正正式式 當選左 再好好計劃下一步<br />\n另一樣就係 各位當選既區議員 希望你地真係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紮紮實實咁做好地區工作</span></span><br />\n比你做得一屆 但係你無實際政績 hea做 浪漫主義 不切實際 咁去盲目追求唔同既政治目標都係唔可取<br />\n下一屆就算你係自己人 你做得差 當區選民都好難再選返你<br />\n唔好睇少蛇齋餅 香港人好<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">善忘</span></span> 大家要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保持警惕</span></span> 真係要日日告誡自己 係三省吾身果隻<br />\n條路係<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">好難行</span></span> 而且中共會用唔同手段 警鄉黑等搞9我地 不過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地放心</span></span> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就算幾難行 我地手足會一齊同你行</span></span><br />\n其次，唔好重複犯錯 以前有立法會議員當選之後即刻買左部ps4 紅酒 係立法會個辦公室 呢類咁7 on9既野 希望唔好再發生 <br />\n最後亦都係最重要既 就係 <br />\n運用你地既<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>資源</strong></span></span>去<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">培育</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">支援</span></span>我地既<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手足 義士</span></span><br />\n不斷去增加我地抗爭既資源 增加政府既管治成本<br />\n繼續壯大我地既版圖 將建制追殺至永無翻身之日<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d2a226c65a017e3d4869c745425d996d2c189ed1","tid":1753634,"uid":122059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:46:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ebb121e8cc41bdb10c0d0122cc0a421b25c4ade","tid":1753634,"uid":122059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:51:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47fee67cf2e1756b595e8b350754b4c3142194c7","tid":1753634,"uid":127807,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0ebb121e8cc41bdb10c0d0122cc0a421b25c4ade","tid":1753634,"uid":122059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:51:28.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:55:31.000Z","msg":"最好出一封EMAIL TEMPLATE<br />\n等大家自己改<br />\n然後SEND比自己區議員<br />\n叫佢地半年內公開PROPOSAL<br />\n點樣去改革社區同埋18區既區議會<br />\n<br />\n要做執政聯盟啦"},{"pid":"768627e5d0d37b17690d3be2c341ff3117644788","tid":1753634,"uid":127807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:55:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcc7a9c43d51c77587daa3cdd46fb4ae06a5afc8","tid":1753634,"uid":127807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2a226c65a017e3d4869c745425d996d2c189ed1","tid":1753634,"uid":122059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:46:02.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:56:16.000Z","msg":"推多下<br />\nPUSH"},{"pid":"e526cc2a7f2dc3fbd8572d4a6f28f17ea6ff18f5","tid":1753634,"uid":330509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:56:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb0b8ff0b198a14a55c2473bcecc7b662a6a8ad","tid":1753634,"uid":258649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:57:02.000Z","msg":"真，好多區都仲係學生，唔可以偷懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e84e575ac76ec1992f91